{"id":5279,"date":"2012-08-18T01:36:54","date_gmt":"2012-08-18T05:36:54","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=5279"},"modified":"2019-05-20T13:28:12","modified_gmt":"2019-05-20T09:28:12","slug":"abu-huraira-converts-his-mother","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/18\/abu-huraira-converts-his-mother\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Parents: Abu Huraira wins his mother to Islam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: None of the Jews or Christians heard of me but that they loved me. I desired for my mother to be upon Islam but she refused. I told her again but she refused again. I went to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I said, &#8220;Supplicate to Allah for her.&#8221; The Prophet supplicated and I went to her. She answered the door and she said, &#8220;O Abu Huraira, I have embraced Islam.&#8221; I told the Prophet, saying, &#8220;Supplicate to Allah for me and my mother.&#8221; The Prophet said, &#8220;<strong>O Allah, endear your servant Abu Huraira and his mother to the people<\/strong>.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 34<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<em>Hasan\u00a0<\/em>(fair) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0639\u064e \u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064e\u062d\u064e\u062f\u064c \u064a\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0648\u062f\u0650\u064a\u064c\u0651 \u0648\u064e\u0644\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0635\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a\u064c\u0651 \u0625\u0650\u0644\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u062d\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0646\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0623\u064f\u0631\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064f\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0650\u0633\u